  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this project:

        1. Confirming the modification in corneal astigmatism after trabeculectomy with MMC and
           intracameral administration of bevacizumab.

        2. Medium-term follow up (6 months) of the induced corneal astigmatism.

        3. Investigating correlations between postoperative astigmatism, particularly with the
           postoperative IOP.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
